body:
### 🍽️ Diverse Cuisine

Twilight Berry Salad, Braised Potatoes with Venison, Salt-Baked Naga, Hydra Meat Sauce Noodles, and more...

Twilight Forest Caterpillars are never absent;

Twilight-themed teas and desserts;

Twilight alcoholic beverages;

All drinks have placeable models and provide different effects after consumption.

### ✨ New Effects and Mechanics

Each boss has its own unique effects...

Witch's Protection: Gain the Lich's shield protection;

Phantom Form: Ability to pass through blocks;

Sturdy Scales: Reduce incoming damage by a percentage and fixed value;

Flame Breath: Shoot Hydra fireballs when attacking;

Erudite Knowledge: Continuously gain experience points, and some interactions do not consume experience;

Giant's Blessing: Gain attribute boosts;

Blizzard: Attacks inflict freezing effects;

Ice Cloud: You have learned the Snow Queen's skill;

Mushroom Perception: Ability to detect nearby chests;
